## The Switch Track

Pass the variable into the `switch()`, and then provide different `case` tracks for it to follow.

```dart
String day = 'Mon';

switch(day) {
  case 'Mon':
    print('Start of week!');
    break;
  case 'Fri':
    print('Almost free!');
    break;
  default:
    print('Just another day.');
}
```
**Important:** You MUST include the word `break;` at the end of every case!

